    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Langobardorum gentis <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs> filius
                        domni bone recordationis <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, ob salute anime nostre, concessimus in <orgName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Monasteries"
                                >monasterio</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> que edificata esse videtur
                        infra hanc nostram Beneventanam civitatem <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >integras res</rs> quibus fuit Leoprandi ex loco quod vocatur <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/3451"
                            >Collina</placeName> seu <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches"
                            >integras res</rs> que fuit Gualprando in loco <placeName
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property" ref="#places/2320"
                            >Venticano</placeName>, pro quo <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Mention #Inflow #Confiscation #Property_of_persons_without_heirs"
                            >sine heredibus decesserunt</rs> sicut legibus ad sacrum nostrum
                        palatium evenit, in ea videlicet ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc
                        nostrum roboreum preceptum supram phato monasterio eiusque rectores iam
                        dictis rebus integris habere et possidere valeas et a nullo ex nostris
                        iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldis vel a quibuscumque agentibus habeas
                        aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis temporibus possideatis. Quod vero
                        preceptus concessionis ex iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName
                            key="#Notary" ref="#people/3466">Petrus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actus <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventus</placeName> primo anno, mense ianuarii,
                        quarta decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
